structure.unit: AGRICULTURAL SEEDS, FEEDING STUFFS, AND FERTILIZERS

law.history: Repealed 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 96. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1719a-14.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Registration of feeding stuff under misleading name or below standard may be refused.
